<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja" prefix="og: http://ogp.me/ns#">
	<head>
		<title><%= title %></title>

		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
		<% if (categoryFileNames !== undefined) { %>
		<meta name="w0s:amazon" content="<%= categoryFileNames %>" />
		<% } %>
		<meta property="og:title" content="<%= title %>" />
		<meta property="og:type" content="article" />
		<% if (ogImage !== null) { %>
		<meta property="og:image" content="<%= ogImage %>" />
		<% } else { %>
		<meta property="og:image" content="https://blog.w0s.jp/image/site-icon.png" />
		<meta property="og:image:width" content="360" />
		<meta property="og:image:height" content="360" />
		<% } %>
		<meta property="og:url" content="https://blog.w0s.jp/<%= page.query.entry_id %>" />
		<meta property="og:locale" content="ja_JP" />
		<meta property="og:site_name" content="富永日記帳" />
		<% if (description !== null) { %>
		<meta property="og:description" content="<%= description %>" />
		<meta name="twitter:card" content="summary" />
		<meta name="twitter:site" content="@SaekiTominaga" />
		<% } %>

		<link rel="alternate" href="/feed" type="application/atom+xml" title="「富永日記帳」の新着フィード" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="/style/blog.css" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="/style/layout_full.css" title="通常表示" />
		<link rel="alternate stylesheet" href="/style/layout_reader.css" title="リーダー表示" id="stylesheet-print" />

		<script src="/script/trusted-types.js"></script>
		<script src="/script/blog.mjs" type="module"></script>
		<% if (tweet) { %>
		<script src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async=""></script>
		<% } %>
		<script src="https://analytics.w0s.jp/matomo/matomo.js" async=""></script>
		<script src="/script/analytics.js" defer=""></script>
	</head>
	<body itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Blog">
		<div class="l-page">
			<%- include('./_include/_header', { heading: false }) %>

			<div id="content" class="l-content">
				<div class="l-content__main">
					<article class="p-entry" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/BlogPosting">
						<header class="p-entry__header">
							<div class="p-entry-header-title">
								<h1 itemprop="name"><%= title %></h1>
							</div>

							<dl class="p-entry-header-date c-entry-meta">
								<div class="c-entry-meta__group">
									<dt>投稿</dt>
									<dd><time datetime="<%= created.format('YYYY-MM-DDTHH:mm:ssZ') %>" itemprop="datePublished"><%= created.format('YYYY年M月D日') %></time></dd>
								</div>
								<% if (lastUpdated !== null) { %>
								<div class="c-entry-meta__group">
									<dt>最終更新</dt>
									<dd><time datetime="<%= lastUpdated.format('YYYY-MM-DDTHH:mm:ssZ') %>" itemprop="dateModified"><%= lastUpdated.format('YYYY年M月D日') %></time></dd>
								</div>
								<% } %>
							</dl>
						</header>

						<main class="p-entry__body" itemprop="articleBody"><%- message %></main>

						<footer class="p-entry__footer">
							<% if (categoryNames.length >= 1) { %>
							<section class="p-entry-footer-category">
								<h2 class="p-entry-footer-category__hdg">カテゴリ</h2>

								<ul class="p-entry-footer-category__list">
									<% for (const categoryName of categoryNames) { %>
									<li><a href="/category/<%= encodeURI(categoryName) %>" rel="tag"><%= categoryName %></a></li>
									<% } %>
								</ul>
							</section>
							<% } %>

							<ul class="p-entry-footer-social c-flex -buttons">
								<li class="c-flex__item">
									<a href="/feed" type="application/atom+xml" class="c-button -feed">
										<img src="/image/icon/feed.svg" alt="" width="16" height="16" class="c-button__icon" />
										<span class="c-button__text">フィード</span>
									</a>
								</li>
								<li class="c-flex__item">
									<a href="https://github.com/SaekiTominaga/blog.w0s.jp/issues/new?title=%5B<%= page.query.entry_id %>%5D%20<%= encodeURI(title) %>;labels=comment" class="c-button -github">
										<img src="/image/icon/github.svg" alt="(GitHub)" width="16" height="16" class="c-button__icon" />
										<span class="c-button__text">コメントを書く</span>
									</a>
								</li>
								<li class="c-flex__item">
									<button type="button" is="w0s-share-button" class="c-button -share">
										<span class="c-button__text">記事のシェア</span>
									</button>
								</li>
							</ul>

							<% if (relations.length > 0) { %>
							<section class="p-entry-footer-relation p-box">
								<h2 class="p-box__hdg">関連記事</h2>

								<ul class="c-grid -wide">
									<% for (const relation of relations) { %>
									<li class="c-grid__item">
										<div class="c-entry-link">
											<a href="<%= relation.id %>">
												<span class="c-entry-link__thumb">
													<% if (relation.image_internal !== null) { %>
													<picture>
														<source type="image/avif" srcset="https://media.w0s.jp/thumbimage/blog/<%= relation.image_internal %>?type=avif;w=180;h=120;quality=60, https://media.w0s.jp/thumbimage/blog/<%= relation.image_internal %>?type=avif;w=360;h=240;quality=30 2x" />
														<source type="image/webp" srcset="https://media.w0s.jp/thumbimage/blog/<%= relation.image_internal %>?type=webp;w=180;h=120;quality=60, https://media.w0s.jp/thumbimage/blog/<%= relation.image_internal %>?type=webp;w=360;h=240;quality=30 2x" />
														<img src="https://media.w0s.jp/thumbimage/blog/<%= relation.image_internal %>?type=jpeg;w=180;h=120;quality=60" alt="" class="c-entry-link__image" />
													</picture>
													<% } else if (relation.image_external !== null) { %>
													<img src="<%= relation.image_external %>" alt="" class="c-entry-link__image" />
													<% } else { %>
													<img src="/image/noimage.svg" alt="" width="180" height="120" class="c-entry-link__image" />
													<% } %>
												</span>
												<span class="c-entry-link__title"><%= relation.title %></span>
											</a>
											<div class="c-entry-link__date">
												<time datetime="<%= relation.created.format('YYYY-MM-DDTHH:mm:ssZ') %>"><%= relation.created.format('YYYY年M月D日') %></time>
											</div>
										</div>
									</li>
									<% } %>
								</ul>
							</section>
							<% } %>
						</footer>
					</article>
				</div>

				<% if (categoryFileNames === 'train') { %>
				<div class="l-content__footer">
					<aside class="p-box" aria-labelledby="bookcm-heading">
						<h2 class="p-box__hdg" id="bookcm-heading">著書の紹介</h2>

						<ul class="c-grid -wide">
							<li class="c-grid__item p-item">
								<a href="https://w0s.jp/tokyu/book/7700">
									<picture>
										<source type="image/avif" srcset="https://media.w0s.jp/thumbimage/blog/book/7700_cover.jpg?type=avif;w=160;h=160;quality=50, https://media.w0s.jp/thumbimage/blog/book/7700_cover.jpg?type=avif;w=320;h=320;quality=30 2x" />
										<source type="image/webp" srcset="https://media.w0s.jp/thumbimage/blog/book/7700_cover.jpg?type=webp;w=160;h=160;quality=50, https://media.w0s.jp/thumbimage/blog/book/7700_cover.jpg?type=webp;w=320;h=320;quality=30 2x" />
										<img src="https://media.w0s.jp/thumbimage/blog/book/7700_cover.jpg?type=jpeg;w=160;h=160;quality=50" alt="" width="114" height="160" loading="lazy" class="p-item__image" />
									</picture>
									<span class="p-item__title">東急7700系形態分類</span>
								</a>
								<div class="p-item__text">
									<p>
										<b>自費出版、<time datetime="2019-08">2019年8月</time>発売</b>
									</p>
									<p>池上線、東急多摩川線で活躍した東急7700系の形態バリエーションについて、2010年時点の在籍車36両を徹底解析しました。</p>
								</div>
							</li>
							<li class="c-grid__item p-item">
								<a href="https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/480220695X?tag=w0s.jp-22&amp;linkCode=ogi&amp;th=1&amp;psc=1">
									<img src="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/51uD92OAjNL._SL160_.jpg" srcset="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/51uD92OAjNL._SL320_.jpg 2x" width="111" height="160" alt="" loading="lazy" class="p-item__image" />
									<span class="p-item__title">東急電鉄 1989-2019 <img src="/image/icon/amazon.png" alt="(Amazon)" class="c-link-icon" /></span>
								</a>
								<div class="p-item__text">
									<p>
										<b>イカロス・ムック、<time datetime="2019-08">2019年8月</time>発売</b>
									</p>
									<p>平成時代の東急電車の動向をまとめた本です。「現役車両ガイド」の一部の本文解説を担当しました。</p>
								</div>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</aside>
				</div>
				<% } %>
			</div>

			<%- include('./_include/_sidebar') %><%- include('./_include/_footer') %>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
